{"tid":910084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鏞記被指碎件拼砌出$100燒鵝麵　鏞記：為品質而用2隻燒鵝的不同部位","createTime":"2018-11-21T01:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T02:15:17.000Z","uid":31798,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95de32a3a693052d39353427a62de14e7fe7111b","tid":910084,"uid":31798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:47:31.000Z","msg":"上回講到：<br />\n鏞記$100燒鵝麵被指「切頭切尾」拼出來　前DJ：請尊重下自己的老字號<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/909128/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/909128/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2210000/2212499/goose3_thumb_20181120_E_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2210000%2F2212499%2Fgoose3_thumb_20181120_E_1024.jpg&h=39696011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前電台DJ及旅遊達人何嘉麗光顧鏞記燒鵝遇上不愉快經歷，指每碗$100的燒鵝麵用上不同鵝隻、不同部位、頭頭尾尾拼出燒鵝，直指是不尊重食客。鏞記發言人回應事件指，碟頭飯或粉麵會選一份骨的部位及一份肉的部位給客人，盡量來自同一隻燒鵝，但不排除為了食物的品質而選取2隻燒鵝的不同部位。<br />\n<br />\n何嘉麗在facebook圖文並茂指：<br />\n<br />\n你由相片嗰度已經見到呢碟燒鵝啲皮係唔同色嘅，即係唔單止來自唔同部位，亦都可能係來自唔同嘅鵝係拼砌而成！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">不過鏞記發言人回應指，鏞記的燒鵝是以炭燒的方法烹調，炭燒的過程中，即使是同一隻鵝受熱程度不一樣，燒鵝皮亦會因此有機會顏色不一致。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指，凡於鏞記點選1隻／半隻／例牌燒鵝，保證絕對是來自同一隻燒鵝，並不會以幾隻不同的燒鵝拼湊而成。</span><br />\n<br />\n至於碟頭飯或粉麵，處理方法是將一隻燒鵝分為8-10等份，再選取一份骨的部位及一份肉的部位給客人，滿足食客的需求。<span style=\"color: red;\">發言人說，盡量是用同一隻燒鵝，但不排除為了食物的品質而選取2隻燒鵝的不同部位。</span><br />\n<br />\n鏞記又指，食客如果對於燒味斬件部位有任何不滿意，可以即時反映，<span style=\"color: red;\">會盡量滿足食客的要求，有需要時更會為食客免費更換（髀位除外）。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地信唔信?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730d7762b45df2ec2f5fb1ef347fb14a7ae29ee0","tid":910084,"uid":31798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:51:37.000Z","msg":"凡於鏞記點選1隻／半隻／例牌燒鵝，保證絕對是來自同一隻燒鵝，並不會以幾隻不同的燒鵝拼湊而成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁果碗麵d鴨即係....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff7b48cddb7eec814e0b7351948e2af8d2483aa6","tid":910084,"uid":121580,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"730d7762b45df2ec2f5fb1ef347fb14a7ae29ee0","tid":910084,"uid":31798,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T01:51:37.000Z","msg":"凡於鏞記點選1隻／半隻／例牌燒鵝，保證絕對是來自同一隻燒鵝，並不會以幾隻不同的燒鵝拼湊而成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁果碗麵d鴨即係....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:07:52.000Z","msg":"麵個d就算la<br />\n人地斬例斬淨咪俾你lol<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56263288208c1912c349e22dfafb7fbe8a392df6","tid":910084,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"一舊水食人餸頭餸尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"354221e79e7435f91ff695bb9b5373ce3f6dcbbe","tid":910084,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"56263288208c1912c349e22dfafb7fbe8a392df6","tid":910084,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:10:48.000Z","msg":"一舊水食人餸頭餸尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n六神合體"}]}